SyntheticaDockbarSlidePanelUI
public class BasicDockbarSlidePanelUI
extends DockbarSlidePanelUI
implements java.beans.PropertyChangeListener

Basic UI implementation for JYDocking dockbar slidePanel.

Optional UI-properties:

  • JYDocking.slidepanel.opaque - Boolean, default is true.
  • JYDocking.slidepanel.left.insets - Insets if placement is left, default is 0,0,0,2.
  • JYDocking.slidepanel.bottom.insets - Insets if placement is bottom, default is 2,0,0,0.
  • JYDocking.slidepanel.right.insets - Insets if placement is right, default is 0,2,0,0.

    • Version:
    1.01, 25.07.2009
